	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002201_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<!--
<p rend="right"><placeName>Newstead Abbey,</placeName><lb/></p>
<p rend="right"><placeName>Mansfield, Notts.</placeName><lb/></p>
-->
				<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>23 Feby 1865 </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Foster</persName>
<lb/>I ought to have 
<lb/>thanked you long 
<lb/>ago for your kindness 
<lb/>in searching for &amp; 
<lb/>sending me the very 
<lb/>copy of the journal
<lb/>I needed - but I have 
<lb/>been so busy that 
<lb/>the duty has been 
<lb/>neglected till I need 
<lb/>your help again 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002201_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>trusting that you are 
<lb/>of a merciful 
<w>dis-<lb break="no"/>position</w> I have to beg 
<lb/>that you will 
<w>for-<lb break="no"/>ward</w> the following 
<lb/>enquiry to <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi>
<lb/>Simmonds</persName> at your 
<lb/>convenience - Whether 
<lb/>the amount of 
<lb/>ivory brought into 
<lb/>the markets of the 
<lb/>world now is as 
<lb/>great as in 1853 
<lb/>or when he wrote the 
<lb/>letter to you after 
<lb/><persName>Professor Owen's</persName>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002201_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/>lecture - <add place="above">in 1857</add> I cannot 
<lb/>make out whether 
<lb/>the amount he 
<lb/>quoted included 
<lb/>all that goes from 
<lb/><placeName>East Africa</placeName> to 
<lb/><placeName>India</placeName> &amp; <placeName>China</placeName> &amp; 
<lb/>as I mean to 
<lb/>quote his statement 
<lb/>in a footnote 
<lb/>I should very 
<lb/>much like to 
<lb/>know if he 
<lb/>thinks the amount 
<lb/>now obtained 
<lb/>from all countries 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002201_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/>be equal to 10,000 cwts<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>It makes a destruction 
<lb/>of some 30 000 
<lb/>elephants necessary<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Will you kindly 
<lb/>forward this 
<lb/>enquiry to him 
<lb/>and ask him to 
<lb/>excuse my 
<lb/>intrusion<reg>.</reg></p>
				<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>I am Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p>Very faithfully 
<lb/><persName>David Livingstone </persName></p>
			
